| ============================================================
| chess.damg — DAMAGE Chess Engine v1.0
| Author: Ultiminium
|
| USER FUNCTIONS:
|   @chess_init    — set up board, pick color
|   @chess_display — print board to terminal
|   @chess_move    — input your move in SAN (e.g. e4, Nf3, O-O)
|   @chess_bot     — engine calculates and returns best move
|
| INTERNAL FUNCTIONS (chess__ prefix, do not call directly):
|   @chess__eval          — score current position across all 8 priorities
|   @chess__priority1     — immediate risks (3-move horizon)
|   @chess__priority2     — forced mates
|   @chess__priority3     — potential mates
|   @chess__priority4     — counter checks
|   @chess__priority5     — promotion
|   @chess__priority6     — potential checks
|   @chess__priority7     — piece count
|   @chess__priority8     — piece value
|   @chess__make          — apply a move to the board
|   @chess__unmake        — reverse a move from the board
|   @chess__push          — push a minimax stack frame
|   @chess__pop           — pop a minimax stack frame
|   @chess__minimax       — drive the 30-ply search loop
|   @chess__san_parse     — parse SAN input into from/to squares
|   @chess__attacks       — check if a square is attacked by a color
|   @chess__in_check      — detect if a king is in check
|
| BOARD:
|   64 vars: chess_a1..chess_h8
|   Piece codes: wP wR wN wB wQ wK bP bR bN bB bQ bK  0=empty
|
| PIECE VALUES:
|   P=100  N=300  B=310  R=500  Q=900  K=20000
|   (scaled x100 to allow fractional positional bonuses as integers)
| ============================================================

| ── Global state ─────────────────────────────────────────────
@var+
     chess_turn+w-
     chess_player+w-
     chess_move_input+e4-
     chess_bot_move+e4-
     chess_status+ok-
     chess_result+ongoing-

     | make/unmake temps
     chess__from+a1-
     chess__to+a1-
     chess__piece+0-
     chess__captured+0-
     chess__sq+a1-
     chess__tmp+0-
     chess__tmp2+0-

     | SAN parse outputs
     chess__san_from+a1-
     chess__san_to+a1-
     chess__san_piece+P-
     chess__san_promotion+0-

     | eval outputs (each priority sets this)
     chess__eval_score+0-
     chess__p1_score+0-
     chess__p2_score+0-
     chess__p3_score+0-
     chess__p4_score+0-
     chess__p5_score+0-
