     | minimax stack (30 plies = depth 0..29)
     chess__depth+0-
     chess__max_depth+30-
     chess__best_score+0-
     chess__best_from+a1-
     chess__best_to+a1-
     chess__node_score+0-
     chess__alpha+-99999-
     chess__beta+99999-
     chess__stack_depth+0-

