| ── @chess__p8_piece_value ───────────────────────────────────
| Priority 8: raw material balance from white's perspective
| white pieces add value, black pieces subtract
| Output: chess__p8_score
@addfunc+
@dyn,var+
@dyn:(chess__p8_score) = 0
@-
| count all 64 squares
@var+
     chess__p8_squares+a1,b1,c1,d1,e1,f1,g1,h1,a2,b2,c2,d2,e2,f2,g2,h2,a3,b3,c3,d3,e3,f3,g3,h3,a4,b4,c4,d4,e4,f4,g4,h4,a5,b5,c5,d5,e5,f5,g5,h5,a6,b6,c6,d6,e6,f6,g6,h6,a7,b7,c7,d7,e7,f7,g7,h7,a8,b8,c8,d8,e8,f8,g8,h8-
@-
| iterate — DAMAGE comma lists iterate with @loop
| We enumerate all 64 manually for precision
if, (chess_a1) = wP
     @dyn,var+
     @dyn:(chess__p8_score) = (chess__p8_score)(+)100
     @-
